// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-2170 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 58229f20-27b3-54da-9d56-b5b18bd37964

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:7*")
